              The Wallet page shows the total amount of Theta and Tfuel on a wallet, the wallet addresses, and a history
              of all the transactions made on that wallet.
              Finding a wallet can be done by using the wallet address, <a href="#domain">domain</a>, or by connecting to a wallet using the <a
                    target="_blank" href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/Theta-wallet/ckelpdlfgochnkdgikcgbimdcfgpkhgk">official
